project_descr: Development of the National Strategic Plan (2011-2015) on HIV/AIDs for Malaysia.

outputs.output_descr: The initiative seeks to assist the government in developing an overall national strategic framework to address the HIV/AISD epidemic. It comprises of the development of three strategic documents - draft National Strategy on HIV and AIDS, draft National Action Plan and draft National Monitoring and Evaluation Framework. All 3 documents will then be presented to the government for consideration to be adopted as the National Strategy for HIV and AIDS for the duration of 2011  2015.
